transcript:
Customer: Hello
Executive: Ji, awaz aa rahi hai abhi mam?
Customer: Ji ji, good morning mam.
Executive: Hello. Abhi aa rahi hai awaz aapko?
Customer: Haan mam aa rahi hai.
Executive: Ji ji, actually aapko services regarding maine connect kiya tha.
Customer: Kya?
Executive: Bataiye mam.
Customer: Mam aapki awaz abhi bhi aa rahi hai, pehle nahi aa rahi thi.
Executive: Theek hai, mujhe aapki shayad break ho ke aa rahi thi. Actually mam aapko services regarding maine connect kiya tha. Last time aapka discussion hua tha TrustSeal. First aapka issue tha TrustSeal ka right? Ki aapko hard copy nahi mili thi.
Customer: Ye koi issue maine, mam maine aapko bataya mujhe koi issues nahi hai. Sara issue khatam ho gaya tha. Maine usi din aapko bata diya tha.
Executive: Nahi nahi, last time apna discussion hua tha ki aapke TrustSeal ke regards bhi maine mam apne senior manager ke sath discuss kiya. Pehle aapko call karne se pehle hi main wo discuss karne gayi thi. To abhi unhone apni side se wo jo raise kara concern, to jaldi aapko shayad response mil jaye uske regarding. Waise aapko issue nahi hua na hard copy?
Customer: Deepanshi ji, Unikanshi ji, main aapko batau? Aapke paas ek diction mein site se Chandan ji the, Varun ji the, Raghav ji the, ek Sardar ji the. Char log aapke pehle se hamare account manager aur charo logo ne aap se pehle process karwa dala hai pura. TrustSeal ka process hona hai, ho gaya hai, ho gaya hai, ho gaya hai. Please khatam kariye mam, please.
Executive: Nahi mam, mam please meri baatein suniye. Dekho wo unki koshish thi mam. Kya pata meri koshish main kar du mam. Dekho ye cheezo ka kya hota hai ki dekho.
Customer: Koshish kar, do teen kya theek hai mam, koshish kar di hogi.
Executive: Nahi nahi, main to sirf, mam ek minute. First cheez main aapse ye puch rahi hu, nahi mili na aapko?
Customer: Abhi tak? Kitni baar main bolu mam, kitni baar bolu ki nahi mili tabhi main complaint kiya. Maine char saal ho gaye mam mujhe na milte milte.
Executive: Jaldi main aapko jaldi call karke response karungi. Bilkul koi issue nahi hai, hum kara denge.
Executive: Aur mam services regarding, services regarding aapko koi issue wagera ho?
Customer: Koi issues nahi hai mam.
Executive: Kaisi chal rahi hai waise services aapki?
Executive: Thoda sa kam active dikh rahi hai.
Customer: Bahut badhiya.
Executive: Kya issue aaya mam, wo bhi to puch rahi hu main.
Customer: Koi issues nahi hai mam, please. Dekhiye hum baar baar wahi kehte hai. Mam koi issue nahi hai. Aap sahi se leads de rahi hai, sahi se hamara kaam chal raha hai. Mera bahut sahi hai. Bas khatam hone dijiye paanch saal hai.
Executive: Bas. Dekhiye mam kya hoti hai, dekhiye mam hamara kaam hota hai aapko connect karna. Right? Dekhiye.
Customer: Mam main manti hu ki aapne connect kiya. Mam dekhiye aapne connect kiya, maine aapko jo tha wo sahi report de di. Baat khatam ho gayi, khatam, khatam na mam.
Executive: Ek to cheeze mujhe aap update karwati hai. Dekhiye mam main manti hu ki aapko buyleads mein, main wahi puch rahi hu buyleads mein koi issue ho to bataiye na. Aap bata rahe hai na ki kuch bhi nahi chal raha hai. Aapne mujhe yahi wording boli thi starting mein. Kuch bhi nahi chal raha to matlab buyleads mein issue aa raha hai, kya issue aa raha hai, wahi puch rahi hu main aapse.
Customer: Deepanshi ji ye bataiye paanch saal ke textile se agar ek lakh ka bhi supply na ho paya IndiaMART se to IndiaMART bekar hai ki achcha hai?
Executive: Kya hua hai?
Customer: Paanch saal ki textile ka maine contract liya tha aur lagbhag ek lakh rupya diya hai aur ek lakh rupya paanch saal mein bhi na nikal paye aisi buyleads aap log dete hai to ye achcha hai ki bekar hai? Aap bataiye ji sahi se karke.
Executive: Dekhiye main manti hu aapko dekho seedhi si baat hai na conversion nahi milta hai to dekho sabhi supplier ko ye issue to bilkul mujhe bolenge. To wahi main puch rahi hu ki aap mujhe concern actual concern bataiye ki aapko matlab buyleads mein issue aa raha hai ya phir post par response aata hai unpe kuch issue aa raha hai. Buyer aapse kya discussion hota hai aapka jo conversion nahi ho paata hai?
Executive: Buyleads mein kya issue aata hai aapko matlab?
Customer: Ek to aati nahi hai, sahi chal raha hai. Abhi mera season chal raha hai, mujhe abhi time nahi hai. Main khali season mein aapse baat karungi. Abhi season chal raha hai, mere jo school days chalte hai pehle se usko main dekhu phir main aapse baad mein baat karungi. Leads aapki aa rahi hai, thank you mam ab aapka jo koshish hai uske liye bhi thank you.
Executive: Mam last, ek baar baat suniye, sirf last ek minute de dijiye mujhe, sirf meri ek baat sun lijiye aap.
Customer: Haan ji.
Executive: Aapne jo product add kiye hai embroidery school logo wale jo abhi aapne update kiye hai na shayad.
Customer: Hmm.
Executive: First mam dekhiye ek to cheeze mujhe aapki taraf se dekho catalog scoring aapka 44 hai, right? Ab ye scoring aapko thoda theek karna padega. Dekho scoring hamara kya rehta hai kam se kam 85 scoring hona chahiye. Uske baad hi aapko buyleads bhi achchi dikhengi aur conversion bhi matlab achcha dikhega. Post ka flow bhi direct aapko zyada ho jaata hai. Dekho abhi catalog score kaafi kam hai 44 hai, product ki information proper tarike se related nahi hai. Abhi aap thoda sa time denge mujhe ki jaise ki video meeting se hum discuss kar paye ki aap kis tarike se better conversion.
Customer: Nahi nahi, bilkul mere paas mam abhi mere paas bilkul time nahi hai, please. Abhi bura mat maniyega, abhi bilkul time nahi hai mere paas. Mujhe production bhi dekhna rehta hai, yaha bhi dekhna rehta hai.
Executive: Aap jab kabhi bhi free ho na mam, dekhiye.
Executive: Ji ji, aap kabhi bhi free ho 10 minute hardly mujhe 10 minute ka time ho aapko mere liye ya phir apne business ke regarding online ke liye to mujhe aap please connect karna. Theek hai? Main aapko WhatsApp pe hi karti hu.
Customer: Okay okay.
Executive: Thank you.
summary:
Concerns:

- Customer has not received TrustSeal hard copy.

- Customer is not getting enough supply from IndiaMART.

- Customer says catalog score is low.



Resolution:

- Executive will check on TrustSeal delivery.

- Executive offered a video meeting to improve conversion.



Next Steps: 

- Executive will follow up on WhatsApp.

refund
